about.summary: ODE solvers and adjoint sensitivity analysis in PyTorch.

name: torchdiffeq
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "torchdiffeq" %}
{% set version = "0.0.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 093be5bdb9c1a81fe3b318ae4dd2c09b33d70f545e55a6d24066b9adb1da8568

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - pytorch-cpu

test:
  imports:
    - torchdiffeq
    - torchdiffeq._impl

about:
  home: "https://github.com/rtqichen/torchdiffeq"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "ODE solvers and adjoint sensitivity analysis in PyTorch."
  doc_url: https://pypi.org/project/torchdiffeq/#description
  dev_url: https://github.com/rtqichen/torchdiffeq

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ndmaxar
    - rluria14
    - oblute
